<subSubSection box="[199,1316,1985,2010]" pageId="1" pageNumber="205" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1436,1588,2010]" box="[199,1316,1985,2010]" pageId="1" pageNumber="205">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,1985,2009]" pageId="1" pageNumber="205">Etymology.</emphasis>
The name refers to the distinct colouration of the forewings; Greek: phaneros—visible.
